        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2021/08/COPO-Camaro-Goes-Big-For-2022-2.jpg",
        "width": 1920,
        "height": 1080,
        "caption": "photo credit: Chevrolet"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It should go without saying these COPO Camaros aren’t street legal. However, you can use them to compete in NHRA Stock and Super Stock. They’re available through Chevrolet Performance as a part.",
